(106.7) have united for a food drive for the Los Angeles Regional Foodbank. 
Through June 19, Moby Disc's seven Southern California stores will give 
discounts of up to $5 per item purchased for those donating canned food. . . . 
The Shubert Theater is taking $5 off ticket prices for Faye Dunaway and Rex 
